# Container/build entrypoints must stay LF on every platform. This repo uses
# core.autocrlf=true on Windows; without this, a fresh checkout rewrites these
# files to CRLF and BuildKit can mishandle backslash-continued Dockerfile
# instructions (baking a stray CR into ENV values → boot failure).
Dockerfile      text eol=lf
*.Dockerfile    text eol=lf
*.sh            text eol=lf
